    <p class="text-gray-300">The operations in the evaluation stage depend on the recoding of the scalar k, which at this point in the algorithm satisfies 0 &lt; k &lt; r. Let t = dlog<sup>2</sup> (r)/(w&minus;1)e, then with notation as in Algorithm 1, the scalar can be written as</p>

